Installation instructions:

On the Cray system:
- svn checkout https://svnemc.ncep.noaa.gov/projects/nceplibs/sp/tags/v2.0.2/
- create module files for the new versions in .../nwprod/lib/modulefiles/
- cd into src folder 
- module load PrgEnv-intel sp-intel craype-sandybridge
- module list 2>compile-intel.log
- ./makelibsp.sh_CrayLinux &>>compile-intel.log
- module switch PrgEnv-intel PrgEnv-cray
- module switch sp-intel sp-cray-haswell
- module switch craype-sandybridge craype-haswell
- module list 2>compile-cray.log
- ./makelibsp.sh_CrayLinux &>>compile-cray.log

